<exercise id="secfhsst_id483"><title> The Doppler Effect for Sound 2 </title>
      <problem id="probfhsst_id484">
      <para id="id232827">What is the frequency heard by a person driving at 15 m<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mo>·</m:mo></m:math>s<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:math> toward a factory whistle that is blowing at a frequency of 800 Hz. Assume that the speed of sound is 340 m<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mo>·</m:mo></m:math>s<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:math>. </para>
      </problem>
      <solution id="solfhsst_id487"> <list id="listfhsst_id487" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic" class="stepwise">
      <item> <label> Determine how to approach the problem based on what is given </label>
      <para id="id232898">We can use</para>
      <equation id="id232902">
        <m:math overflow="scroll" mode="display">
          <m:mrow>
            <m:msub>
              <m:mi>f</m:mi>
              <m:mi>L</m:mi>
            </m:msub>
            <m:mo>=</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>v</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:msub>
                  <m:mi>v</m:mi>
                  <m:mi>L</m:mi>
                </m:msub>
              </m:mrow>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>v</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:msub>
                  <m:mi>v</m:mi>
                  <m:mi>S</m:mi>
                </m:msub>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:msub>
              <m:mi>f</m:mi>
              <m:mi>S</m:mi>
            </m:msub>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
      </equation>
      <para id="id232955">with:</para>
      <equation id="id232960">
        <m:math overflow="scroll" mode="display">
          <m:mtable displaystyle="true">
            <m:mtr>
              <m:mtd columnalign="right">
                <m:mi>v</m:mi>
              </m:mtd>
              <m:mtd>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              </m:mtd>
              <m:mtd columnalign="left">
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>340</m:mn>
                  <m:mspace width="0.166667em"/>
                  <m:mi mathvariant="normal">m</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mi mathvariant="normal">s</m:mi>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                      <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                    </m:mrow>
                  </m:msup>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:mtd>
            </m:mtr>
            <m:mtr>
              <m:mtd columnalign="right">
                <m:msub>
                  <m:mi>v</m:mi>
                  <m:mi>L</m:mi>
                </m:msub>
              </m:mtd>
              <m:mtd>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              </m:mtd>
              <m:mtd columnalign="left">
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>15</m:mn>
                  <m:mspace width="0.166667em"/>
                  <m:mi mathvariant="normal">m</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mi mathvariant="normal">s</m:mi>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                      <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                    </m:mrow>
                  </m:msup>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:mtd>
            </m:mtr>
            <m:mtr>
              <m:mtd columnalign="right">
